---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import SchemaMarkup from '../../components/SchemaMarkup.astro';
import Icon from '../../components/Icon.astro';

const publishDate = "November 26, 2025";
const author = "The Valley Clean Team";
const readTime = "10 min read";
---

<BaseLayout title="New Year Deep Clean 2025 | Valley Clean Team" description="Ring in 2025 with a spotless home. Complete guide to deep cleaning your Alabama or Tennessee home for a fresh start.">
  <SchemaMarkup type="article" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-12 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <span class="category-tag">New Year Cleaning</span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">
          <Icon name="calendar" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />{publishDate}
        </span>
        <span class="text-gray-500 text-sm ml-4">
          <Icon name="clock" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />{readTime}
        </span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#333333] text-center leading-tight">
        New Year Deep Clean: Start <span class="gold-gradient">Fresh in 2025</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        There's no better way to welcome a new year than with a spotlessly clean home. Here's your complete guide to refreshing your space and starting 2025 with clarity and calm.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <article class="py-12 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          As the holiday decorations come down and the champagne flutes get washed, there's a unique energy in the air. January represents possibility—a blank slate, a fresh start. And for many of us in Huntsville, Nashville, Birmingham, and across North Alabama and Tennessee, that fresh start begins at home.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
          A deep-cleaned home isn't just about appearances. Research shows that clean, organized spaces reduce stress, improve focus, and even help us sleep better. What better way to set yourself up for success in the new year than with a home that feels refreshed and renewed?
        </p>

        <div class="bg-[#FFA985]/10 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8 border-l-4 border-[#FFA985]">
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-2">
            <Icon name="quote-left" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Did You Know?
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            A Princeton University study found that clutter actually competes for your attention, reducing your ability to focus and increasing stress levels. A clean home literally helps you think more clearly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Why Now Section -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="calendar-check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Why January is the Perfect Time for a Deep Clean
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          While spring cleaning gets all the attention, January actually offers some unique advantages for tackling a whole-house deep clean:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="snowflake" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mr-2" />You're Home More
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              Cold weather keeps us indoors, giving us time to tackle projects. Plus, you'll actually enjoy the results of your hard work!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="tree" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mr-2" />Holiday Chaos is Over
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              The decorations are down, guests have gone home, and your schedule is finally your own again.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="brain" class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500 mr-2" />Fresh Start Mindset
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              The "new year, new me" motivation is real. Channel that energy into your home!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">
              <Icon name="dollar-sign" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />Post-Holiday Sales
            </h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
              Cleaning supplies, organizational products, and storage solutions are often on sale in January.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The 2025 Reset Method -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="redo" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          The 2025 Reset: A Room-by-Room Deep Clean Guide
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          This isn't your typical cleaning checklist. The 2025 Reset is about more than surface cleaning—it's about creating a home that supports the life you want to live this year. We'll tackle each area with three goals: <strong>Clean</strong>, <strong>Declutter</strong>, and <strong>Organize</strong>.
        </p>

        <!-- Kitchen -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-10 mb-4">
          <Icon name="utensils" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
          The Kitchen: Command Center Reset
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          After weeks of holiday cooking and entertaining, your kitchen has earned a serious deep clean.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Deep Clean Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean inside the refrigerator—toss expired items, wipe shelves</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Deep clean the oven (self-clean cycle or manual scrub)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean microwave inside and out</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Degrease range hood and filters</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Run dishwasher cleaner through an empty cycle</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub sink and polish faucet</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean cabinet fronts and handles</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash trash can inside and out</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Deep clean floors, including under appliances</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-blue-100">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
            <Icon name="box-open" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Declutter Challenge:
          </h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Toss expired pantry items and spices</li>
            <li>• Donate gadgets you never use</li>
            <li>• Recycle old plastic containers with missing lids</li>
            <li>• Clear out that "junk drawer" and start fresh</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Bathrooms -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-10 mb-4">
          <Icon name="bath" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
          Bathrooms: The Spa Treatment
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          After hosting holiday guests, your bathrooms deserve some serious TLC.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Deep Clean Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub grout lines (use a grout brush and cleaner)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Remove hard water stains from shower doors and fixtures</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean exhaust fan cover</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Scrub toilet thoroughly (base, behind, and tank)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash shower curtain or liner</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean inside drawers and cabinets</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash all towels, bath mats, and linens</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean mirrors until streak-free</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-blue-100">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
            <Icon name="box-open" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Declutter Challenge:
          </h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Toss expired medications (dispose safely)</li>
            <li>• Throw away old makeup and skincare products</li>
            <li>• Donate unused toiletries</li>
            <li>• Replace worn towels and washcloths</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Bedrooms -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-10 mb-4">
          <Icon name="bed" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
          Bedrooms: Your Sanctuary Refresh
        </h3>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Better sleep is one of the most popular New Year's resolutions. A clean, organized bedroom supports that goal.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Deep Clean Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash all bedding (sheets, pillowcases, blankets, duvet cover)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Flip or rotate your mattress</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Vacuum the mattress and under the bed</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash pillows (most are machine washable!)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Dust ceiling fan blades and light fixtures</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean windows and window sills</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Dust all furniture, including tops of dressers and nightstands</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Vacuum or mop floors, including closet floors</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6 border border-blue-100">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
            <Icon name="box-open" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" />Declutter Challenge:
          </h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Go through your closet—donate what you haven't worn in a year</li>
            <li>• Clear nightstand clutter</li>
            <li>• Sort through dresser drawers</li>
            <li>• Remove excess decorative items from surfaces</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Living Areas -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-10 mb-4">
          <Icon name="couch" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2" />
          Living Areas: Gathering Space Revival
        </h3>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Deep Clean Checklist:</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Vacuum upholstery and under cushions</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Spot clean or steam clean fabric furniture</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wash throw blankets and pillow covers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Dust all surfaces, shelves, and decor items</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean TV screen and electronics</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Wipe down light switches, door handles, and remotes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean windows inside</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Deep clean carpets or rugs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="square" class="w-3 h-3 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" />
              <span class="text-gray-700">Clean baseboards</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Often Forgotten Areas -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="eye-slash" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Often Forgotten Areas (Don't Skip These!)
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          A true deep clean includes spots we overlook during regular cleaning:
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985]/10 to-gray-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Light switch plates</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Door handles and knobs</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Ceiling fans</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Air vents and registers</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Behind toilets</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985]/10 to-gray-100 rounded-xl p-4">
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Under furniture</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Window tracks</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Top of refrigerator</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Inside trash cans</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-2 mt-1" />
                <span>Garage entry floor</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Mental Benefits -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="brain" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          The Mental Health Benefits of a Clean Home
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          This isn't just about aesthetics. Here's what science tells us about clean spaces:
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border-l-4 border-[#FFA985]">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Reduced Stress</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Studies show that people with cluttered homes have higher levels of cortisol (the stress hormone) throughout the day.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border-l-4 border-[#FFC67D]">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Better Sleep</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">The National Sleep Foundation found that people who make their beds are 19% more likely to report getting a good night's sleep.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border-l-4 border-green-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">Improved Focus</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Visual clutter competes for your attention, making it harder to concentrate on tasks. A tidy space = a clearer mind.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md border-l-4 border-blue-500">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-2">More Productivity</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700">When you're not searching for lost items or distracted by mess, you get more done in less time.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Creating Lasting Habits -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="sync" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Making It Last: Cleaning Habits for 2025
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          A January deep clean is great, but maintaining that fresh feeling requires ongoing effort. Here are simple habits to keep your home clean year-round:
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985]/10 to-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Daily (10-15 minutes)</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>• Make your bed</li>
            <li>• Wipe down kitchen counters after cooking</li>
            <li>• Load/unload the dishwasher</li>
            <li>• Quick tidy of living spaces before bed</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Weekly (1-2 hours)</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
            <li>• Vacuum/mop all floors</li>
            <li>• Clean bathrooms</li>
            <li>• Change bed linens</li>
            <li>• Dust surfaces</li>
          </ul>

          <h4 class="font-bold text-[#333333] mb-4">Monthly</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>• Deep clean one room (rotate through your home)</li>
            <li>• Clean inside refrigerator</li>
            <li>• Wash windows</li>
            <li>• Declutter one area</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Professional Help -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#333333] mt-12 mb-6">
          <Icon name="hands-helping" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3" />
          Start the Year Right—With Professional Help
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Let's be honest: tackling a whole-house deep clean while recovering from the holidays, getting back to work, and managing daily life is a lot. That's where The Valley Clean Team comes in.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Our New Year Deep Clean service covers everything on this list—and more. We'll give your home the thorough reset it deserves so you can start 2025 with:
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <Icon name="star" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#FFA985] mr-3 mt-1" fill="currentColor" />
            <span class="text-gray-700">A sparkling clean kitchen ready for healthy cooking</span>
          </li>
